reviewText: John Branyan  is always great. Only letdowns were that his "Flyover Comedy" was a little longer, and my favorite routine on here I already saw online (that is obviously my own fault). In the additional material, he adds an unusual encouragement as was in the main body of his previous DVD.

I didn't laugh once.
Also, this DVD wouldn't play on my TV's DVD player, though it would play on a personal DVD player.
You tube ruined this for me.
So enjoyable--keep up the good work:)
